The two missiles arrive fast. The first one hits Warhead, but his 
armor allows him to be relatively unharmed, while the second one 
explodes near him, lifting him from the ground.

--- In nbwrpg@y..., RoboRick007 <rfa007@c...> wrote:
> ::Kup::
> 
> He sees that one of his shots hit the beast, but is hesitent to fire 
again, and put Sunhawk in more danger.
> 
> ::Hot Rod::
> 
> With a blur of red, and dust cloud not far behind, Hot Rod arrives. 
He quickly transformes to bot mode, and looks around. He sees Warhead 
laying in stasis.
> 
> "I'll take that one out first..."
> 
> Hot Rod locks on and fires two missiles at Warhead's, near lifeless 
body.
